name: AND.ALSO x Windfall Jewellery Palm Tree & Pineapple necklace and stackable rings
description:
AND.ALSO has teamed up with Windfall Jewellery to bring you a range of tropical jewellery for your fruity hands and necks.

Each piece is handmade all the way from Melbourne in Windfall Jewellery studio using sterling silver.

The rings come as a set: so you get not only the pineapple but the palm tree too. So keep them both for the perfect set or share with a pal and give your buddy a taste of the tropics too. Share the love.
